thumb.title: Blonde eyelash wash
thumb.description: (hannah May 4, 2022)Made this all on stream in a day to meet the jacoldoer deadline, fairly happy with the results but the more i try to extend the video the more i despise it. I don't think I will be working any more on this video, but i won't delete the pf+clips yet to keep hope alive :) #viol2022 #JacolEC #Heavenat47th unlisted + delisted y'all know what that means :) shout out to everyone who pulled through and chatted even for a lil last 2 streams, they was a lot of fun. and shout out pals.:) i got another version on my computer but im publishing this from the iphone and cba to rerender4k lol IF I EVER make another shoegaze edit that'll be crazy best belive it, i think next will be 2 SALEM though
